# The basic [[unit]] of [[length]] in the [[International System of Units]] (SI: Système International d'Unités). It is equal to {{frac|39|47|127}} (approximately 39.37) [[imperial system|imperial]] [[inch]]es.
#* '''1797''', ''The Monthly magazine and British register'', No. 3
#*: The measures of length above the '''metre''' are ten times ... greater than the '''metre'''.
